{"tid":2065962,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：下午公布最新失業率料將上升","createTime":"2020-06-16T03:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T07:49:27.000Z","uid":166360,"like":124,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"a5fecfa3167d6b3436bc3aac2ee1315128e6120b","tid":2065962,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T03:05:44.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥：下午公布最新失業率料將上升<br />\n2020-06-16 HKT 10:01<br />\n<br />\n政府下午將公布3月至5月的失業率，行政長官林鄭月娥表示，數字一定會上升，對上一次公布的失業率是5.2%，希望社會留意上升幅度有否放緩。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，政府提出龐大的「保就業」計劃是希望令失業不要惡化，目前因失業領取社署綜緩的個案，升幅已放緩，指出有關個案在今年年初曾大幅上升，3月按月的升幅超過10%，4月更按月升24%，5月則升1.4%。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，目前因失業領取綜緩的個案超過1萬8千宗，自己離任社署署長時的有關個案數目遠比目前高，希望經濟衰退及失業情況不會好像沙士時期一般差。她又說，隨香港疫情趨穩定，政府會進一步放寬社交距離措施，加上星期日開始接受市民申請一萬元，希望增加市民本地消費，整體經濟情況或有所改善，希望社會保持信心。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532303-20200616.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532303-20200616.htm&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7re6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=b0a6aefc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532303-20200616.htm&h=81dbe270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532303-20200616.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">The New Great Depression Is Coming...</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"bacf4397621c0db7897605828efe4e470bd5bf6e","tid":2065962,"uid":128923,"like":59,"dislike":2,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T03:06:31.000Z","msg":"繼續立國安法 加速制裁 唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c28b58664a08892634edbb3bbea2e298498797b","tid":2065962,"uid":213877,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T03:06:41.000Z","msg":"幾高都無用啦<